flowchart TB
    Dev([Developer]):::actor -->|git push| Hook{{Webhook}}
    Hook ==> Build

    subgraph CI [CI Pipeline]
        direction TB
        Build[/Build &amp; Compile/] --> Test{Tests pass?}
        Test -->|yes| Scan[[Security Scan]]
        Test -->|no| Fail((Fail))
        Scan --> Image[(Container Image)]
    end

    subgraph CD [CD Pipeline]
        direction TB
        Stage[Deploy Staging] --> Smoke{Smoke OK?}
        Smoke -->|yes| Prod[Deploy Production]
        Smoke -->|no| Rollback>Rollback]
    end

    Image ==>|promote| Stage
    Prod --> Released(((Released)))
    Fail -.->|notify| Dev
    Rollback -.->|alert| Dev

    classDef actor fill:#1f6feb,stroke:#ffffff,color:#ffffff
    classDef danger fill:#da3633,stroke:#ffffff,color:#ffffff
    class Fail,Rollback danger
